ate timeout awaiting response at Redis endpoint redis-cart:6379.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio and server_error_ratio; error_ratio jumped from 0.0% to over 28%, indicating possible service disruption or overload.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend-1 error_ratio median changed from 0.0% to 28.06% and p99 to 31.03%.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis responded with drastic increase in rrt (round trip time), indicating possible IO bottleneck or saturation; latency (rrt) increased from 153.95 ms to 7067.19 ms median.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis-cart-0 rrt median increased to 7067.19 ms, and p99 to 109222375.41 ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Drop in request and response rates significantly, possibly due to scaling issues or service throttling by upstream dependencies.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Productcatalogservice-2 requests dropped from 8366 to 573.5 median, fanning out across dependent services.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency increase for cartservice demonstrated by rrt_max rising to over 5993119.5 ms.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Cartservice-0 rrt reached a median of 1632790.68 ms and rrt_max soared to 5993119.5 ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased client_error_ratio suggests possible failovers or misconfiguration affecting service stability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Shippingservice-0 client_error_ratio p99 reached 47.5%.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"The cartservice showed excessive latency while accessing redis